# 1
```
  flowchart TB
    A["Pod is scheduled to one node"]
    B["Local kubelet / containerd calls Cilium CNI"]
    C["Local cilium-agent programs that node<br/>veth, Pod IP, endpoint state"]
    D["Other nodes learn how to reach<br/>and identify this Pod"]
    E["They update routing, Service,<br/>and Policy state as needed"]
    F["Pod traffic goes through the eBPF datapath"]
    G["eBPF handles routing, Service LB, and Policy"]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G

```